{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"body":"Fix pushed as Gerrit change 746 (https://rebar.solutions.navateam.com/c/rebar/+/746), stacked atop 741. RE-ASSESSMENT (fixed build, signing live): ALL authored event types now sign through the shared finalize_event seam — CREATE, COMMENT, EDIT, FILE_IMPACT, STATUS(transition/claim/close), claim EDIT all show author_sig; 'rebar verify-identity --all --require-authenticated' exits 0 (every enforced event verifies). Held-out oracle 5/5 + teeth (mutating out finalize_event -> transition/close tests go RED). ruff+mypy clean. Full suite: 6217 passed / 3 failed — the 3 failures are config-show/perf tests that detect this machine's ~/.config/rebar/config.toml (from 79da) via a test-isolation gap; they PASS with that file absent and on CI (fresh runner). NOT a regression from this change. Follow-up ticket filed for the isolation gap."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1784249110548224001,"uuid":"50349147-58fa-4776-a879-cfd0c4b49f9a"}